title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show SEP-04-2013 WED
description:
The Glenn Beck Program - 09/04/13 








The Glenn Beck Program is Live Monday - Friday from 9am - 12pm ET,


Doc Thompson fills in for Glenn Beck.
 Doc talks about Obama gathering together Washington's leadership to vote on Syria,
 which is bad news for everyone.

 Doc asks if this means we're allying ourselves with Al Quaeda.

 Also, Nancy Pelosi's conversation with her grandson only proves how wrong she is.
